==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gravimetric
<hw>Grav"i*met"ric</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to measurement by weight; measured by
weight.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Grav"i*met"ric*al*ly</wf> <pr>(#)</pr>,
adv.</wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Gravimetric analysis</b></col> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>,
<cd>analysis in which the amounts of the constituents are determined by
weight; -- in distinction from <cref>volumetric
analysis</cref>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>gravimetry</ent>⟦br⟧
